    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      277.63,
      96.59,
      337.4,
      109.87
    ],
    "text": "Judgement",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      124.61,
      143.3,
      137.89
    ],
    "text": "Introduction",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      152.61,
      543.15,
      165.89
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner is a body cooperate, incorporated under the laws of Sri Lanka, and is capable of",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      180.36,
      543.15,
      193.64
    ],
    "text": "suing and being sued in its corporate name. It has been duly registered and issued with a license to",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      207.89,
      539.97,
      221.17
    ],
    "text": "carry out the business of life insurance, which in insurance terminology is referred to as a \u2018long-",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      235.64,
      280.38,
      248.92
    ],
    "text": "term insurance\u2019 business within Sri Lanka.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      274.22,
      546.22,
      288.44
    ],
    "text": "In the course of its business, the Petitioner engages the services of insurance agents. The 4th",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      302.66,
      542.58,
      315.94
    ],
    "text": "Respondent was once recruited as such an agent; however, after working for a few weeks, he",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      330.41,
      542.68,
      343.69
    ],
    "text": "claimed a salary which the Petitioner refused to pay, giving rise to a dispute. Following a complaint",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      356.99,
      454.7,
      371.21
    ],
    "text": "made by the 4th Respondent to the 1st to 3rd Respondents, an inquiry was held.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      397.68,
      543.15,
      410.96
    ],
    "text": "Without giving due notice to the Petitioner, the Respondents held the inquiry and ordered the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      424.24,
      543.1,
      438.49
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner to pay the salary claimed by the 4th Respondent. In addition to that the Respondents have",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      452.71,
      414.92,
      465.99
    ],
    "text": "instituted proceedings in the Magistrate Court based on the said order.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      492.46,
      543.2,
      505.74
    ],
    "text": "In those circumstances, the Petitioner has instituted the above-styled Application in this Court, and",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      519.98,
      543.13,
      533.26
    ],
    "text": "after the issuance of formal notice the Respondents have filed their respective Objections, except",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      546.79,
      543.08,
      561.01
    ],
    "text": "the 4th Respondent, who did not appear despite notices duly issued. This was argued before me on",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      575.23,
      246.35,
      588.51
    ],
    "text": "10.12.2025; hence, this judgement.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      614.76,
      399.68,
      628.04
    ],
    "text": "The following arguments were advanced by Counsel at the hearing.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      654.51,
      132.3,
      667.79
    ],
    "text": "Arguments",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      724.78,
      312.13,
      754.09
    ],
    "text": "4",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      71.65,
      543.16,
      85.87
    ],
    "text": "Mr. Hatch, learned P.C. contended that the 4th Respondent, being an insurance agent, cannot be",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      100.09,
      543.07,
      113.37
    ],
    "text": "considered as an employee of the Petitioner. He heavily relies on the Regulation of Insurance",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      127.86,
      543.12,
      141.14
    ],
    "text": "Industry Act, No. 43 of 2000 (hereinafter referred to as the \u201cRII Act\u201d), and the definition given",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      155.36,
      542.8,
      168.64
    ],
    "text": "therein in support of his submissions. In addition to that, he brought to my notice by referring to",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      182.17,
      543.06,
      196.39
    ],
    "text": "the application made by the 4th Respondent to the Commissioner, as he has not sought EPF or ETF,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      210.64,
      407.92,
      223.92
    ],
    "text": "except for the salary, which is marked as R1 annexed to the Petition.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      245.2,
      543.08,
      259.42
    ],
    "text": "Having referred to R2 and R3, it is his position that though the 4th Respondent has made an",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      273.91,
      543.2,
      287.19
    ],
    "text": "application to the Commissioner of Labour, the Petitioner has never turned up for any inquiry as",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      301.41,
      317.63,
      314.69
    ],
    "text": "the said documents had not been received by him.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      337.16,
      542.96,
      350.44
    ],
    "text": "In addition to that, he referred to R4, which is a part of the proceedings before the Commissioner,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      363.74,
      543.16,
      377.96
    ],
    "text": "and brought it to the notice that the 4th Respondent\u2019s affidavit is not an affidavit. He further argued",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      392.18,
      542.81,
      405.46
    ],
    "text": "that no shred of evidence is placed before the Commissioner to establish that he is an employee of",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      419.93,
      142.3,
      433.21
    ],
    "text": "the Petitioner.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      455.46,
      543.19,
      468.74
    ],
    "text": "On the other hand, Ms. Nayomi Kahawita argued that the Petitioner has not represented or made",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      482.96,
      543.12,
      496.24
    ],
    "text": "any representation to the Attorney General to make arrangements to expedite the matter without",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
